## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential bias in sources advocating for or against steroid use. Additionally, the ethical considerations and health implications are complex and may vary depending on individual circumstances and the specific context of use. Further research, including longitudinal studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term effects and ethical considerations of steroid use in sports.

